description: Enhancing Inter-Ethnic Community Dialogue and Collaboration in FYR Macedonia

subproject.description: Key national and local institutions in 3 micro-regions dealing with inter-ethnic relations have a system to address issues that may weaken inter-ethnic cohesion; civil society is better able to participate in, and establish mechanisms that promote cultural diversity, and multi – cultural and civic identity.
